attachments.title: Uncorked Studios Blog iOS 7 Background Effects And Split View Controllers
attachments.text: IOS 7 offers many interesting effects like transparency and blur on interface elements. While the system handles many of these effects automatically, UISplitViewController seems to have been left out. In this post you will see how to create transparency and blur effects on a split view controller and do so in a performant manner.
